product_name: MilaniHighly Rated Lash Extensions Tubing Mascara
summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsCruelty FreeVeganGive BackMilani's Highly Rated Lash Extensions Tubing Mascara delivers the look of lash extensions with technology that wraps each lash in tube-like polymers to add instant length and lift.
details: DetailsFeaturesTube-like polymers extend every lashShea Butter & Castor Seed Oil help nourish and condition lashesCruelty-FreeMade in USABenefitsFlake-free tubing mascara for instantly longer & lifted lashes*16-hour, clump-proof, smudge-proof wear*Effortlessly removes with just warm water93% had instantly lifted, longer-looking lashes*Lash extending tubing technology forms individual tubes around each lash to create instant length & lift* for the look of lash extensions*Consumer Panel ResultsItem 2605150How To UseStart with the wand at the base of lashes and sweep from root to tip to coat, define and lengthen every lash.To remove, gently splash warm water a few times to ensure eyes are wet. Using a gentle motion, take pointer finger and thumb and gently wiggle and pull to remove tubes while eyes remain closed. Wash away any remaining product with warm water and/or face wash.IngredientsWater / Aqua / Eau, Acrylates/Ethylhexyl Acrylate Copolymer, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Glycerin, Alcohol Denat., Dimethicone, VP/Eicosene Copolymer, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax / Copernicia Cerifera Cera / Cire de carnauba, Stearic Acid, Laureth-50, Jojoba Esters, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax, Acacia Decurrens Flower Wax, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Synthetic Beeswax, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Niacinamide, Caulerpa Lentillifera Extract, Polyglycerin-3, Tocopherol, Palmitic Acid, Methylglucamine, Ethylhexylglycerin, Cellulose, Hectorite, Disodium EDTA, Butylene Glycol, Tromethamine, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Phenoxyethanol, Iron Oxides (CI 77499).
how_to_use: Start with the wand at the base of lashes and sweep from root to tip to coat, define and lengthen every lash.To remove, gently splash warm water a few times to ensure eyes are wet. Using a gentle motion, take pointer finger and thumb and gently wiggle and pull to remove tubes while eyes remain closed. Wash away any remaining product with warm water and/or face wash.
ingredients: Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax / Copernicia Cerifera Cera / Cire de carnauba

reviews.headline: I recommend for school
reviews.comments: when you apply it and then look it gets on your eyelid and if you blink there's smudges under your eyes. BUT once it dries, i don't get any smudging or flaking throughout the day. i do find it very lengthening but slightly clumpy. the tubing effect makes my dreaded evening makeup removing soo much easier!

reviews.headline: Clumps
reviews.comments: Wand does not seperate but clumps.

reviews.headline: Would buy again!
reviews.comments: This product is excellent it does get on my eyelid when applying but I'm able to get it off pretty easy. I would buy this product again great length and easy to remove.

reviews.headline: Longer Length, Even Longer Drying Time
reviews.comments: I can only use tubing mascaras; everything else smudges for me. This mascara gives me the best length of any tubing mascara I've tried. The problem is that it takes forever to dry. I have to be very, very careful for about ten or fifteen minutes after applying this mascara. If I sneeze or blink too hard, it makes a goopy mess under my eyes. Once it's dry, it's great!

reviews.headline: Yes
reviews.comments: Love it

reviews.headline: Not a fan.
reviews.comments: Color is good. Tough application. Cannot come back later and just swipe another coat because it has hardened on the eyelashes.

reviews.headline: Would not recommend
reviews.comments: I was really hoping I would like this tubing mascara.  I didn't like it.  It is very wet.  I have used it twice.  Each time I applied this mascara it made such a mess on my eyelids.  I wear contacts and it got in my eyes and really irritated them.

reviews.headline: Absolutely not
reviews.comments: I have no idea how this product has 4 stars. This has to be one of the absolute worst mascaras i have ever used. It is so wet and clumpy, and weighs down my lashes. Strongly do not recommend

reviews.headline: Worst
reviews.comments:
This is the worst mascara I have ever purchased. It doesn't thicken or add length at all. If you're going for a natural look where it looks like you don't even wear mascara this is the mascara for you because it just makes my lashes a little bit darker.

I will not be buying again

reviews.headline: No ma'am
reviews.comments: Weird, wet formula. Weighed my lashes down. Threw it out.

reviews.headline: BEST MASCARA! ESPECIALLY FOR STRAIGHT LASHES!
reviews.comments: I'M NOT EVEN KIDDING WHEN I SAY GO BUY THIS! RIGHT NOW!!  I have pin straight lashes and I've tried like every kind you can try  and non of them worked, until I tried this!! GO BUY IMMEDIATELY!

reviews.headline: Game Changer
reviews.comments: Tubing mascaras are great and this one is so affordable and bold. Only downside is the end of the bottle tends to get a little piecey but a great buy!

reviews.headline: better than expected
reviews.comments: I was impressed with the look and performance of this mascara.  I didn't think that a mascara at this price would be such a high quality product. I will definitely be buying this repeatedly and recommending it to all of my friends!!!!

reviews.headline: Not my fav
reviews.comments: Was not impressed with this formula, way too wet and clumpy. Will not be repurchasing

reviews.headline: Almost got an eye infection from this mascara
reviews.comments: Its a great volume mascara but way to watery which caused macara to get in my eye i had to take out with my fingers if i wasnt able to get it out i would have probably got an infection in my eye

reviews.headline: didn't like
reviews.comments: Only thing I liked is that it comes with a lot of product. It did not make my lashes long

reviews.headline: I loved this mascara and would buy it again.
reviews.comments: This mascara is really good, it doesn't smear and it is easy to take off. It also makes my lashes look amazing!

reviews.headline: Horrible mascara
reviews.comments: I love tubing mascara but this is possibly the worst product I have ever used. The formula is extremely wet and takes forever to dry. You cant buidl it up at all. I wouldn't recommend this mascara at all.

reviews.headline: I would definitely buy again
reviews.comments: This is a highly lengthening mascara and really does the job. I'm more of a volume+ lengthening girly, but this only gave lengthening. Also, sometimes it gives spider lashes. If you want to double coat, let the 1st coat dry, then do the 2nd. It's affordable and we'll worth your money. SO easy to get off

reviews.headline: I've had better tubing mascaras
reviews.comments: I minused two stars because the mascara was clumpy and watery.  However l, it is very pigmented and removes super fast. For the price, i would say its okay.

faceoff_positive.comments: I love my new Milani Cosmetics - Highly Rated Lash Extensions Mascara. It definitely makes my lashes look fuller and longer. I love that it stays on my lashes and never flakes off on my face. It truly makes my lashes look extended. It easily comes off with my makeup remover wipes. I highly recommend this mascara if you are looking for a premium product that is definitely going to give you a longer, fuller lash look.
faceoff_positive.headline: Longer Lashes

faceoff_negative.comments: I loved the tubing mascara idea it gives my lashes great lengths however I wouldn't say it give the appearance of lash extensions. Even though I curl my lashes throughly they still end up dropping almost instantly after applying mascara. I so like how easy it is to wipe off/remove.
